      "Text": "Security update for python3",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for python3 fixes the following issues:\n\n- python36 was updated to 3.6.13\n- CVE-2021-23336: Fixed a potential web cache poisoning by using a semicolon in query parameters use of semicolon as a query string separator (bsc#1182379).\n",
